## Python Style Guide

### PEP 8 Compliance

This project follows [PEP 8](https://pep.python.org/pep-0008/).

**Key Points:**
- Indentation: 4 spaces
- Line length: 88 characters
- Encoding: UTF-8
- Imports: Grouped (standard, third-party, local)

## Naming Conventions

### Variables and Functions
```python
# Good
user_id = 123
def get_user_by_id():
    pass

# Bad
userId = 123  # camelCase
def GetUserById():  # PascalCase
    pass
```

### Classes
```python
# Good
class UserService:
    pass

# Bad
class user_service:  # snake_case
    pass
```

### API Endpoints
```python
# Good - kebab-case for URLs
/api/v1/user-profiles
/api/v1/order-items

# Bad
/api/v1/userProfiles  # camelCase
/api/v1/order_items   # snake_case
```

